I've wanted to punch him
for a long time, just watch.

246
00:30:44,739 --> 00:30:47,540
Today, I'm going to pinch his ankle.
I'm going to squeeze his nape.

247
00:30:47,540 --> 00:30:51,780
I'll give him a good beating first.

248
00:30:52,499 --> 00:30:55,179
Did Jiang Chang Yang get ready
with everything for ending it?

249
00:30:55,179 --> 00:30:56,979
How dare he?

250
00:31:05,499 --> 00:31:07,580
What are you doing?

251
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:09,800
What are you doing?

252
00:31:12,499 --> 00:31:16,330
We gambled that the first to marry is a dog.

253
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:19,520
Now, I concede.

254
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:27,480
Please accept these gambling winnings, my lady.

255
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:29,800
So much money.

256
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:40,179
Weren't they already married?
Why give her the money today?

257
00:31:40,179 --> 00:31:45,780
If you came back for the money,
didn't you say so beforehand?

258
00:31:45,780 --> 00:31:50,080
You were sleeping so soundly.
How could I bear to wake you up?

259
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:53,580
I just thought that if you woke up and saw so much money,

260
00:31:53,580 --> 00:31:55,760
you would be happier.

261
00:31:56,340 --> 00:31:59,699
Don't talk nonsense. Everyone is here.

262
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:03,780
Let's go back first.

263
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:05,580
Let's go.

264
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:09,039
Come on. Stop looking and hurry up.

265
00:32:18,659 --> 00:32:23,380
Wasn't it all confiscated before?
Where did so much money come from?

266
00:32:23,380 --> 00:32:26,919
What corrupt official
doesn't have multiple hiding places?

267
00:32:28,659 --> 00:32:31,100
Did you only come back for the money?

268
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:34,440
I got up early and even made a trip to the palace.

269
00:32:35,739 --> 00:32:37,380
I have arranged it with Mr. Third.

270
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:41,359
Once we purge Prince Ning's faction, he'll give me
a position that allows for inspections everywhere.

271
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:45,640
Wherever your shop opens, I'll follow.

272
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:51,319
In the future, you won't be able to shake me off
even if you wanted to. Don't regret it.

273
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:56,879
I won't regret it for this wager I won.

274
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:04,039
You aggressively brought people
to storm the Jiang Mansion.

275
00:33:04,039 --> 00:33:07,380
Do you think I regretted it after sobering up?

276
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:09,480
I didn't.

277
00:33:13,419 --> 00:33:17,140
Tell me, were you trying to scare me on purpose?

278
00:33:17,140 --> 00:33:21,280
How could I? Moving so much money
made my hands sore.

279
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:25,240
Jiang Chang Yang, what are you doing?

280
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:28,440
It's broad daylight. Put me down.

281
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:32,359
Put me down, I'll walk myself. What are you doing?

282
00:33:42,939 --> 00:33:44,639
What are you doing?

283
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:57,259
If you get angry someday and take it out on this,

284
00:33:57,259 --> 00:33:59,219
there's still half left.

285
00:33:59,219 --> 00:34:04,040
This way, you won't regret and feel sad
to find the token destroyed after you calm down.

286
00:34:09,780 --> 00:34:12,199
I wasn't taking it out on it.

287
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:16,480
I just saw that you couldn't let go of me
but were too afraid to be with me.

288
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:19,220
So I helped you cut off the thoughts.

289
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:22,939
This way, you won't feel sad every night,
holding this hairpin.

290
00:34:22,939 --> 00:34:28,519
Yes, yes, Lady He is the most decisive.
How could I escape from your clutches?

291
00:34:30,499 --> 00:34:34,579
From now on, you can't escape anymore.
Don't push me away.

292
00:34:34,579 --> 00:34:36,720
And don't leave me.

293
00:34:49,939 --> 00:34:56,080
I wasn't acting impulsively from drunkenness.
I will cherish my life more for you.

294
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:16,779
It looks good.

295
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,450
