written by common scholars from various places?

328
00:39:01,639 --> 00:39:04,340
If His Highness doesn't take this seriously,

329
00:39:04,340 --> 00:39:09,959
I'm afraid the young men from noble families
will find it hard to have a bright future.

330
00:39:11,099 --> 00:39:14,459
Everyone, everyone, please be patient.

331
00:39:14,459 --> 00:39:19,680
His Highness is not at the residence
precisely because he's seeking solutions for you.

332
