Everyone, you can't solely rely on His Highness.

335
00:39:28,380 --> 00:39:32,220
After all, this concerns
the future of your own sons.

336
00:39:32,220 --> 00:39:38,760
Mr. Zhu, as the Minister of Agriculture,
dealing with a few poor scholars should be easy.

337
00:39:39,559 --> 00:39:45,280
I am in charge of warehouses,
not their examination papers.

338
00:39:48,499 --> 00:39:53,780
The Spring Exam is approaching,
and it's the perfect time to study and prepare.

339
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:58,519
